# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback.
# Serve index.html (HTTP 200, no redirect) for any path that doesn't match a
# built asset, so a COLD first-load of /enroll?token=... reaches the app even
# before the service worker is installed. Pages matches real files first, so
# /assets/*.js, /icons/*, etc. are still served directly; only unmatched routes
# fall through here. The query string is preserved, so EnrollmentScreen prefills
# from ?token=. /admin is served the same index.html and routed client-side in
# App.tsx (App.tsx delegates /admin/* to the admin portal).
